    .grater-container
      .grater
        .showtee
          %img{:src => "assets/images/springfling.jpg", :height => "460", :width => "300"}
          %h3.spring Spring Fling
          %p Yale's annual Spring Fling concert is often abbreviated YSF.  The Tee Standard couldn't resist parodying the logo of high-fashion designer Yves Saint Laurent.
        .showtee
          %img{:src => "assets/images/kidswalk.jpg", :height => "460", :width => "300"}
          %h3.kids Kids Walk for Kids
          %p Hearts of Gold, a New York-based charity foundation dedicated to helping homeless mothers and their children commissioned this tee shirt for their annual Kids Walk for Kids fundraiser.
      .grater
        .showtee
          %img{:src => "assets/images/tailgate.jpg", :height => "460", :width => "300"}
          %h3.tailgate The Tailgate Tee
          %p The Tee Standard created this tee shirt alongside its 2011 Yale / Harvard Game shirt to highlight Yaleâ€™s winning streak in the most important part of the Game: the tailgate.
